{"tid":1540281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加大力度講監狗會個機制有幾撚廢","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:22:57.000Z","uid":231993,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a27eb80197a64580735ba614c995ccc895d87410","tid":1540281,"uid":231993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:10:12.000Z","msg":"獨立監察警方處理投訴委員會，簡稱監警會（IPCC）。Richard 重申監警會並無「調查權」，亦無法得到第一手資料。<br />\n所有個案，不論來源，均須交由香港警務處投訴警察課（CAPO）處理及調查，監警會只負責審核報告，以及要求投訴警察課澄清或重新調查可疑個案。<br />\n要加大力度文宣比人知<br />\n點解要成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n因為依家監狗會個機制<br />\n根本係自己人查自己人"},{"pid":"c79de18b8802b859f9df04d51960721291d983c3","tid":1540281,"uid":231993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:10:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2db5a0a88e0cc5a7c78a7a7bc387f5cd7ec038b","tid":1540281,"uid":264717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:10:49.000Z","msg":"大家做左乜你唔知姐<br />\n唔係個個做左野都會周圍同人講<br />\n唔係咩叫Be water <br />\n唔好搞分化"},{"pid":"243fa8b2e693a8adee3efe6a49776266365d8ba1","tid":1540281,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:10:50.000Z","msg":"7婆為自己鋪後路咋！唔好中伏<br />\n<br />\n《777終極自救》加兩條友入監狗會「提供建議」，香港人咁都袋住先？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539900</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0923e1d84a8289f919e9fafc97b32a2d28142d65","tid":1540281,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649ad9a50cd7abf6e13e57e8373ecf785e662641","tid":1540281,"uid":258210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:10:52.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\nbin個袋住先我就同bin個割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a685bcaf0bf3c993f6410e486c1c